              </span>
              <div class="flex-1">
                <p class="font-azeret-mono text-sm mb-2 tracking-wide">
                  Rizky Rahad
                </p>
                <h2 class="font-libre-baskerville text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl leading-snug group-hover:underline transition-all duration-600">
                  Queers Don't Just Shoot Back— We Nurture The Fire
                </h2>
                
                <!-- Hidden content that appears on hover -->
